thread.title: Rachael

author: Rachael
title: Rachael
text: This place is always super clean and the staff is really friendly. The only reason I gave it four out of five stars is because their office hours don't offer a lot of flexibility with normal business hours and its really difficult for me to get there after work in time before they close. They also don't allow use of the carts after the office hours and so i almost always have to bring my own dolly because I can't make it during the office hour time frame.
